m/artists/stevie-nicks">史蒂维·尼克斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondie">黛比·</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/journey">哈利、史蒂夫·佩里</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joan-jett">琼·杰特和黑心乐队</a>等。</p><p>这张唱片以两首翻唱结尾：《Let It Be》，由幸存的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈·斯塔尔</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mick-fleetwood">以及</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-frampton">彼得·弗兰普顿</a>和米克·弗利特伍德演唱；《Free Bird》由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lynyrd-skynyrd">林纳德·斯金纳德</a>成员加里·罗辛顿（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lynyrd-skynyrd-founding-guitarist-gary-rossington-dies-aged-71-3408659">3 月份去世</a>）和阿蒂姆斯·派尔演唱。以及罗尼·范·赞特（Ronnie Van Zandt）死后的声音。</p><p> 《Rockstar》将于 11 月 17 日通过 Butterfly/Big Machine 发行。<a href="https://shop.dollyparton.com/">在此</a>预订专辑。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cu8hS6WsosU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width=