com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Squid-Press-Shots-2023-Alex-Kurunis_11_HiRes-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Squid-Press-Shots-2023-Alex-Kurunis_11_HiRes-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Squid-Press-Shots-2023-Alex-Kurunis_11_HiRes-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Squid-Press-Shots-2023-Alex-Kurunis_11_HiRes-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Squid-Press-Shots-2023-Alex-Kurunis_11_HiRes-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/squid">Squid</a>与 Tim Key 合作录制了 Paul Ewen 的故事<em>Lessons</em>的音频，现在可以收听。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/squid-interview-2023-o-monolith-3451689">Squid 在新专辑《O Monolith》中：“我们现在都处于最佳状态：我们从未如此自信”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这个故事首次出现在乐队上个月发行的新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/squid-o-monolith-review-3452138">O Monolith</a> 》黑胶唱片内的小册子上，而 Squid 吉他手安东·皮尔森 (Anton Pearson) 为英国诗人、编剧和喜剧演员 Key 朗读的音频创作了伴奏音乐。可在<a href="https://squiduk.bandcamp.com/track/lessons-a-story-by-paul-ewen-read-by-tim-key" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bandcamp</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WeFtkjgkiHM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a>上免费收听。</p><p> “我们很喜欢与这两个我们非常敬佩的人一起工作，”皮尔森在一份新闻声明中谈到此次发布时说道。</p><p>您可以在下面收听新的录音。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Squid - 课程：Paul Ewen 的故事，Tim Key 朗读" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WeFtkjgkiHM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在详细阐述此次合作时，Pearson 表示：“John Fahey 在其 1967 年专辑《The Transfiguration of Blind Joe Death》中插入的故事激发了该项目的灵感，在阅读和聆听了 Paul Ewen 的精彩作品（ <em>《伦敦酒吧评论</em>》、 <em>《如何成为公众》）</em>后，Pearson 说道：<em>作者</em>）并与他交谈，我们发现他对我们的工作有很好的理解，并且对该项目有令人兴奋的想法。</p><p> “他说他想写一个关于一位脱离现实的地理老师的故事，没有比这更令人兴奋的了！同样，蒂姆似乎对保罗的幽默有着惊人的把握，他的表达将其提升到了另一个水平，就像酒吧评论系列中的情况一样。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvHeKzWNQzw/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.