42.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/snoop-dogg-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/snoop-dogg-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于编剧和演员持续罢工，<a href="/artists/snoop-dogg">史努比狗狗</a>取消了即将在洛杉矶举行的好莱坞碗演出。</p><ul><li><strong><strong>阅读更多：</strong></strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/how-long-will-the-hollywood-actors-strike-last-3473291">好莱坞演员的罢工会持续多久？</a></li></ul><p>计划在著名的圆形剧场举行的两场演出是为了庆祝这位长滩说唱歌手 1993 年首张专辑《Doggystyle》问世 30 周年。这张开创性的唱片是他的第一张冠军专辑，也是当时销量最快的嘻哈专辑。</p><p>现在，Snoop Dogg（真名 Calvin Cordozar Broadus Jr）在 Instagram 上发布了一份声明，告诉粉丝：“我们很遗憾地通知您，由于罢工仍在继续，而且罢工何时结束的不确定性，我们需要取消好莱坞露天剧场 (Hollywood Bowl)展示。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvINFYARtP6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="t